  "id": "business",
  "name": "Business Landing",
  "description": "Professional landing page with hero, features, testimonials, and a contact section.",
  "category": "business",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>Your Business</title>\n  <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Your Business\">\n  <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Professional services you can trust\">\n  <style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #ffffff; color: #1e293b; }\n    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e3a5f); color: white; padding: 100px 24px; text-align: center; }\n    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); margin-bottom: 16px; }\n    .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.85; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 32px; }\n    .hero a { display: inline-block; background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 99px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: background 0.2s; }\n    .hero a:hover { background: #2563eb; }\n    section { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 24px; }\n    h2 { font-size: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }\n    .features { display: grid; gap: 32px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); }\n    .feature { text-align: center; padding: 24px; }\n    .feature h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 16px 0 8px; }\n    .feature p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; }\n    .testimonial { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px; }\n    .testimonial p { font-style: italic; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n    .testimonial cite { color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 600; }\n    footer { text-align: center; padding: 32px; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"hero\">\n    <h1>Grow Your Business</h1>\n    <p>We help small businesses thrive with tailored solutions that drive real results.</p>\n    <a href=\"#contact\">Get Started</a>\n  </div>\n  <section>\n    <h2>What We Offer</h2>\n    <div class=\"features\">\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <h3>Strategy</h3>\n        <p>Data-driven business strategies that align with your goals and market position.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <h3>Design</h3>\n        <p>Beautiful, conversion-focused designs that make your brand stand out.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <h3>Growth</h3>\n        <p>Marketing and analytics to help you reach the right audience at the right time.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n    <h2>What Clients Say</h2>\n    <div class=\"testimonial\">\n      <p>\"They transformed our online presence. Our leads increased 3x in the first quarter.\"</p>\n      <cite>Sarah Chen, Founder of Bloom Studio</cite>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <footer id=\"contact\">Contact us at hello@yourbusiness.com | Built with Flowin</footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
}
